dct_title_s: Nova et integra Caenomaniae descriptio vulg. la Mans
dct_description_sm: Two bar scales on map given in "Milliaria parua" and "Milliaria magna".
Decorative cartouches, descriptive text in bottom right.
From Cornelis de Jode's Speculum Orbis Terrae, 1593, a re-issue of Gerard de Jode's Speculum Orbis Terrae, 1578.
